      <span class="bg-transparent border border-grey-dark rounded text-sm font-semibold text-grey-dark px-2 py-1 mx-1">
        Ciencia ficción
      </span>
      <span class="bg-transparent border border-orange rounded text-sm font-semibold text-orange px-2 py-1 mx-1">
