      </span>
      <span class="bg-transparent border border-indigo rounded text-sm font-semibold text-indigo px-2 py-1 mx-1">
        Harem
      </span>
      <span class="bg-transparent border border-pink rounded text-sm font-semibold text-pink px-2 py-1 mx-1">
        Musical
      </span>
      <span class="bg-transparent border border-yellow-darker rounded text-sm font-semibold text-yellow-darker px-2 py-1 mx-1">
        Aventura
      </span>
      <span class="bg-transparent border border-indigo-light rounded text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-light px-2 py-1 mx-1">
